title: Morning Hatha Yoga & Pranayama on the Beach
description: Come wake up your mind, body, and soul with a Hatha flow on the beatiful beaches of Canggu
address: Pantai Batu Bolong St, Canggu, North Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali

title: Kundalini Yoga at Canggu Villa
description: This class will include warm-ups, breathing techniques (pranayama), an exercise set (kriya), deep relaxation, chanting, and meditation. This practice helps to balance the glandular system, strengthen the nervous system, expand lung capacity, and purify the blood.
address: 77 Jalan Raya Kayutulang Gang Joya, 80351 Canggu, Indonesia

title: Showing Up: Integrated Men and Women's Circle
description: Have the opportunity to explore and discuss life themes with fellow members of your gender and with the unique opportunity to “show up” for members of the opposite sex as we integrate a men and women’s circle together to allow us to support, share, and see each other as one collective group.
address: Jl. Nelayan No.78F, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, Bali

title: Free Flow Ecstatic Dance
description: An ecstatic dance journey of movement, breath and music
address: Jl. Nelayan No.78F, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, Bali

title: Sound Healing Journey
description: With the use Tibetan Singing Bowls and Crystal Bowls, energy is shifted throughout the body to create calmness, grounding, and clarity. The vibrations create and inspire a feeling of deep relaxation and opening of the inner space. Come and experience a depth of energy & expansion that is profound.
address: Jl. Tirta Tawar No.Br, Junjungan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571

title: Free Guided Morning Meditation
description: Get your day started on the right mental and emotional track. To support positive community growth, I'm offering this free morning meditations class.
address: Jl. Suweta, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571•0878-6108-4707

title: Poolside Hatha Flow at Gorgeous Villa
description: Enjoy a traditional Hatha flow surrounding a tranquil pool, while overlooking the beautiful Ubud greenery
address: Jalan Raya Andong No.72 ZX, Peliatan, Ubud, Gianyar, Petulu, Kecamatan Ubud, Denpasar, Bali

title: Full Moon Kirtan
description: Join us for a heart opening evening of devotion honoring the sacred transformations of reawakening. Kirtan is a form of devotional chanting whose roots go back to India over 500 years. It is a form of Bhakti Yoga (yoga of devotion) and has the power to open the heart. The singing is accompanied by musical instruments and rhythmic drumming while the audience is encouraged to participate by chanting, clapping and dancing. Explore kirtan and bhajans, connecting with the qualities of Indian deities.
address: Jl. Nelayan No.78F, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, Bali

title: Art Therapy through Mandala
description: Designing and coloring mandalas can help you focus your attention, great exercise for calming down your stressed and waking up your mind. They help with balance, bring peace and tranquility, built your concentration, make it easier to be mindful, push aside thought and let your creativity flow. Looking at them will give you feeling of calmness.
address: Jl. Suweta, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571•0878-6108-4707

title: Sunset Beach Hatha Yoga
description: Come join me for a beachside hatha flow at sunset
address: Pantai Batu Bolong St, Canggu, North Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali

title: Ocean of Oneness Yin Yoga & Sound Healing
description: Immerse yourself in an 'ocean of oneness' relaxing and opening therapeutically through a series of deeply held yin postures that will soothe your soul.
address: Jl. Suweta, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571•0878-6108-4707

title: Pranayama & Meditation Workshop
description: Students will  explore breathing yogic breathing and pranayama technique; learn about Tantra Yoga Philosophy, Hatha Yoga, the chakra system and the subtle body and discuss the purpose of pranayama in yoga practice. There will be time to practice different breathing exercises and various pranayama techniques. This workshop is suitable for all levels.
address: Jl. Tirta Tawar No.Br, Junjungan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571

title: Intro to Ayurveda (The Science of Life)
description: Ayurveda – the sister science of yoga, is the holistic medical system of ancient India and offers much more than simple remedies of ailments, it’s a science of putting one’s life into balance with greater nature. In this workshop we will establish a solid understanding of core Ayurveda teachings, as well as individual practical applications that will enhance one’s wellbeing and vitality.
address: Jl. Suweta, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571•0878-6108-4707
